summary:
Born in Argentina, with Italian roots. Currently living in Amsterdam.
My studies as a Psychologist gave me the tools, but my life experience, travelling around the world, getting to know different cultures, made me passionate about people. Listening, understanding, perceiving are my main qualities.
I find myself as a highly motivated person, with the capacity to help creating a very pleasant work environment and enhance the skills of every member of the team i'm a part of.
I’m a responsible and hard-working person looking for new challenges, with a special focus on people development.
In my free time I love to travel, cycle, be with friends, drink coffee, do yoga, and listen to music.
